sc_cat_item.description:
Citrus blend of essential oils derived from pink grapefruit, wild orange, sweet orange and lemon. Formulated to lift your mood, clear your mind and boost your energy.  Oh, and it makes your kitchen smell divine.  

Add a little or a lot to your spray bottle for a natural fragrance that smells, well...natural.

1 bottle can fragrance up to 10 bottles of cleaning spray!
